<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>43</hymn_number>
<author>Patea</author>
<title>Van Lal Cha Thisan</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Jerusalem indan chungnung achun,
 Ka Lalpan a thisan a hawm ie;
 Khutichun, lungngaihna mei zing nuoiah,
 Ka Lal thavai naubang a kap hi.

[V2]
 Aw nanghaw, Jerusalem mite,
 A lungsiet na chanuh heu inla;
 Na nat tincheng uh a hun sukdam sak,
 A lungngaihna hengilh lo zen un,

[V3]
 2. &quot;Jerusalem khuo kulh pawlam achun,
 Thiemgau thih dan ahi puoi&quot; a tiu;
 Mahleh entie, Kalvari lampi khu,
 Mipi lakah ka Lalpa ka mu'i.

[V4]
 3. En tiem u, Kalvari tang chung achun,
 Van Lal cha thisan chu a luong ie;
 Khawvel gitloh cheng thienna ding ahi,
 Van Lal nunnem thisan hung luong chu.

[V5]
 4. Hun hengilh ngei hiel puong ka, Lal Isu,
 Kalvari lam chu hung nga nang ie;
 Kei dinga na thawkna ka lungsung ah,
 Ka nuktan tieng geiin hezing ka.</lyrics>
</song>